    <h1 class="headline-lg">The Digitalancers<br>Platform</h1>
    <p class="section-subtitle">
      Payxem is one platform with three core products for every digital professional: <strong>Payments</strong> (invoices and pay links), <strong>Portfolio</strong> ({username}.payxem.com), and <strong>Digital Business Card</strong> (pxem.link/@username). One signup, one link, one identity.
